{"tid":2126672,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［知法犯法] 男警賣徦波鞋同抗拒海關人員 裁判官杜浩成判80小時社會服務令","createTime":"2020-07-27T03:43:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-05T02:11:55.000Z","uid":321059,"like":14,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"d5429805f52bb7dacfc9e66fd112ff08e515331f","tid":2126672,"uid":321059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T03:43:50.000Z","msg":"25 歲警員涉嫌去年 9 月出售三對假冒的「adidas」波鞋，在港鐵站交收時被海關拘捕，其間反抗並傷及關員。該警員早前承認出售應用偽造商標貨品、管有應用偽造商標貨品作出售用途及抗拒海關人員共 4 項控罪，案件今（27 日）於觀塘裁判法院判刑。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">裁判官杜浩成</span></span>考慮社會服務令報告中<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">顯示被告已汲取教訓</span></span>，並指希望被告明白社會對公職人員有特別要求，稱「所有公職人員應避免成為害群之馬，令其他盡心盡力的公職人員受到影響」，<span class=\"red\">最終判處他履行 80 小時社會服務令。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/3302774389808158/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F710476795704610%2Fposts%2F3302774389808158%2F&d=EOe11knUQePtQJIakN8qx02FGjryiJR74P7%2B0uEOyUg%3D&h=f8ba9e31\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/3302774389808158/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">犯法就係犯法<br />\n除非你係警察</span></span>"},{"pid":"2365bfeb6d341ff05a06846e5196966071c950a1","tid":2126672,"uid":71748,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T03:47:26.000Z","msg":"又可以做返黑警"},{"pid":"2678608443f2ae175be5103989dc2d39149a0d5e","tid":2126672,"uid":50386,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T03:48:18.000Z","msg":"黑狗打傷關員都係80小時社服<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n抗爭者hi到防暴個盾牌都要坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9b702eb229c2ba843fd88bbcc5ca8da9c029efc","tid":2126672,"uid":321059,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T03:48:37.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">杜浩成仲有好多威水史</span></span><br />\n<br />\n裁判官杜浩成曾處理不少社運案的判決引起爭議，包括他<span class=\"red\">早前下令將三名於8.29深水埗電影放映會被捕的未成年中學生，暫交由兒童院「照顧」約一個月</span>，以待福利官撰寫報告，變相令三名年輕人未被落案控告便先遭關押；其後案件交由另一名裁判官處理，裁判官不作任何命令，三人可與家人團聚。<br />\n<br />\n一名蒙面便衣警於元旦晚上在旺角遭多人襲擊。22歲侍應和25歲經理被控一項襲警罪，案件今（12日）在觀塘裁判法院提訊。<span class=\"red\">裁判官杜浩成形容，非法集結的控罪在本案「呼之欲出」，問控方會否加控相關控罪。</span><br />\n<br />\n2012年，青年泰歷在中聯辦外高呼平反六四，與警員衝突，被控襲警罪。雖然並無警員受傷，但杜官指泰歷濫用示威遊行自由作非法行為，重判他入獄半年。翌年他處理古思堯及馬雲祺企圖侮辱區旗案時，裁定兩人罪成還柙。梁國雄庭外批評<span class=\"red\">指有參與愛港力活動撐政府的市民打記者，杜官只罰款1,500元了事；但馬的案件不涉暴力，杜官卻將他還柙。</span>"},{"pid":"826a2b1ad74b225c6bf41cc41550c5ffec085ee7","tid":2126672,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T03:48:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bb0ccd34abaea022f01ecf6d08c5ac053e42db3","tid":2126672,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T03:50:43.000Z","msg":"On 9     80小時社服"},{"pid":"6b29294b328b60bdee5789b9caca01dca9fdbfcd","tid":2126672,"uid":76674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T03:51:57.000Z","msg":"冇判個海關坐一世咪算執到"},{"pid":"cb3616798d02f32b25bd4552446cd479f24798bd","tid":2126672,"uid":321059,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T03:52:33.000Z","msg":"知法犯法嘅香港警察<br />\n賣假嘢打傷埋海關<br />\n先判嗰80小時社服 <br />\n<br />\n三個青年去觀賞會俾狗濫捕<br />\n杜官就未審先判要佢哋入兒童院<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dada7300dd0ed4a70ce3b2e54ae4fbacedfcee2d","tid":2126672,"uid":124277,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T03:53:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"212f3dc102c1cea8744a5ef9412beadf944aa54c","tid":2126672,"uid":68080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T03:54:58.000Z","msg":"反抗並傷及關員<br />\n80社會服務令<br />\n<br />\n所以話軍政府就係咁<br />\n海關？食屎啦"},{"pid":"cbc258a74619fad8bf0709306e33e9008ac999d7","tid":2126672,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T04:11:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f81e505df0ec8ff0bdce1c2c331fc47d0a2915d","tid":2126672,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T04:12:34.000Z","msg":"狗咬水瀨"},{"pid":"943cf33a497cfbec23f0f06a91ed7097c61b2743","tid":2126672,"uid":261545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T04:13:04.000Z","msg":"又是杜浩成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0b6c04f021e7354db7d27b309dace7af87e7cba","tid":2126672,"uid":73340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T04:15:15.000Z","msg":"2012年，青年泰歷在中聯辦外高呼平反六四，與警員衝突，被控襲警罪。雖然並無警員受傷，但杜官指泰歷濫用示威遊行自由作非法行為，重判他入獄半年。翌年他處理古思堯及馬雲祺企圖侮辱區旗案時，裁定兩人罪成還柙。梁國雄庭外批評指有參與愛港力活動撐政府的市民打記者，杜官只罰款1,500元了事；但馬的案件不涉暴力，杜官卻將他還柙。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n12年已經堅守做狗既信念"},{"pid":"b8fd82a6287bb73b022bece97c4d025cd890ba28","tid":2126672,"uid":2383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T04:16:50.000Z","msg":"傑出系列"},{"pid":"c5493e220a883384a1bdb567